(Plakat Jiangqi)

526
00:34:32,360 --> 00:34:33,710
Qiu Ziliang tak mengambilnya?

527
00:34:34,150 --> 00:34:35,440
Milikku telah diambil.

528
00:34:38,080 --> 00:34:40,190
Lalu plakat ini?

529
00:34:40,920 --> 00:34:42,280
Milik Benteng Kiri yang kucuri.

530
00:34:48,800 --> 00:34:49,480
Syukurlah,

531
00:34:49,800 --> 00:34:50,880
