550
00:36:34,990 --> 00:36:38,540
♪Kepiluan masa lalu masih tertinggal♪

551
00:36:38,680 --> 00:36:41,590
♪Mimpi buruk menyibakkan tirai♪

552
00:36:41,690 --> 00:36:46,940
♪Lihat, di antara cinta dan benci
