553
00:36:47,260 --> 00:36:52,900
♪Perubahan yang mengambang♪

554
00:36:53,450 --> 00:36:58,760
♪Tanpamu, segalanya adalah jurang♪

555
00:36:59,580 --> 00:37:02,930
♪Lagi-lagi berpura-pura manis♪

556
00:37:03,100 --> 00:37:05,970
♪Perjalanan jauh♪

557
00:37:05,970 --> 00:37:08,500
♪Tidak boleh berpapasan tanpa alasan♪

558
00:37:08,600 --> 00:37:09,320
Sekarang,

559
00:37:09,760 --> 00:37:11,200
