560
00:37:12,760 --> 00:37:13,440
Yu Niang,

561
00:37:13,800 --> 00:37:14,960
aku ingin memusnahkan kubu kasim,

562
00:37:15,120 --> 00:37:16,200
apa kau bersedia membantuku?

563
00:37:19,000 --> 00:37:20,080
Namaku Wang Ruoling,

564
00:37:21,240 --> 00:37:22,560
merupakan keturunan Wang Yang.

565
00:37:23,040 --> 00:37:25,520
Saat Insiden Embun Pagi, seluruh
keluarga Wang dibunuh.

566
00:37:26,840 --> 00:37:27,600
Sebelumnya,

567
00:37:27,760 --> 00:37:29,520
