00:38:21,680 --> 00:38:24,200
Aku adalah Pemangku Pedang
Biro Ziyi.

576
00:38:29,120 --> 00:38:30,200
Kau bersedia membantuku?

577
00:38:38,280 --> 00:38:39,680
Maksudmu adalah...

578
00:38:40,640 --> 00:38:44,080
ingin menyelamatkan Yang Mulia
Raja Guang terlebih dulu?

579
00:38:49,440 --> 00:38:50,000
Yu Niang,

580
00:38:50,480 --> 00:38:51,400
aku bersedia membantumu.

581
00:38:51,760 --> 00:38:53,240
Mari kita bersama-sama
membasmi kejahatan,

582
00:38:53,840 --> 00:38:55,390
menyingkirkan penjahat di sisi Kaisar.

583
00:39:07,800 --> 00:39:12,120
